  <div class="project-text">
  <div class="project-description">
    Mobile playlist manangement and navigation vary across many
    different mobile applications. Most users either use Spotify,
    Soundcloud, Apple Music, or Google Play. This project was
    designed with 2 other students in an Information Architecture course at
    UCSD, and we created an information architecture wireframe for mobile
    devices. In the 2-week process, my team and I conducted interviews,
    walkthroughs, made a competitive analysis, and created a
    high resolution wireframe.

    </article>
